!! File layout

```
dev-wiki/plugins/rimir/diffsync/
  plugin.info                  -- plugin metadata (v0.1.0)
  icon.tid                     -- SVG icon
  diff-hunks.js                -- library: diff computation, hunks, reconstruction
  diff-hunks.js.meta           -- metadata sidecar
  action-diffsync.js           -- widget: <$action-diffsync> action widget
  action-diffsync.js.meta      -- metadata sidecar
  panel.tid                    -- interactive comparison panel UI
  styles.tid                   -- CSS (ds-* prefix)
  settings.tid                 -- ControlPanel settings tab
  config-context-lines.tid     -- default config: context lines = 3
  readme.tid                   -- plugin readme
  README.md                    -- GitHub-facing readme
  documentation.tid            -- doc-template wrapper
  changelog.tid                -- version history
  LICENSE.md                   -- MIT license
  LICENSE.md.meta              -- license sidecar
  doc/
    overview.tid               -- doc-template overview
    architecture.tid           -- architecture and data flow
    reference.tid              -- widget API, data formats, state tiddlers
    examples.tid               -- usage examples
    dev-workflow.tid            -- this file
```

!! Restart rules

|!File |!Restart needed? |!Why |
|`diff-hunks.js` |Yes |Library module -- cached by TW's module system |
|`action-diffsync.js` |Yes |Widget module -- registered at startup |
|`panel.tid` |No |Wikitext -- re-rendered on each view |
|`styles.tid` |No |Stylesheet -- re-read from wiki store |
|`settings.tid` |No |Wikitext -- re-rendered on each view |
|`config-context-lines.tid` |No |Read per comparison via `wiki.getTiddler` |
|Doc tiddlers (`doc/*.tid`) |No |Wikitext |

!! CSS conventions

All CSS classes use the `ds-` prefix to avoid collisions:

* `ds-panel`, `ds-picker-row`, `ds-picker`, `ds-select` -- layout
* `ds-actions-row`, `ds-apply-row` -- button rows
* `ds-field-section`, `ds-field-header`, `ds-field-name` -- field display
* `ds-toggle-group`, `ds-toggle`, `ds-toggle-source`, `ds-toggle-target` -- source/target toggles
* `ds-field-values`, `ds-field-value`, `ds-field-value-source`, `ds-field-value-target`, `ds-field-selected` -- single-line field values
* `ds-hunk`, `ds-hunk-header`, `ds-hunk-body`, `ds-hunk-source` -- hunk display
* `ds-line-equal`, `ds-line-delete`, `ds-line-insert` -- line-level diff coloring
* `ds-results` -- results container

Theme utility classes (`rr-muted`, `rr-small`, `rr-badge-circle`, `rr-badge-added`, `rr-badge-removed`, `rr-status-info`, `rr-link-btn`, `rr-input-row`, `rr-input`) come from the theme plugin dependency.

!! Dependencies

* `$:/plugins/rimir/theme` -- listed in `plugin.info` `dependents`; provides `rr-` utility classes
* TW core `diff_match_patch.js` -- used by `diff-hunks.js` via `require()`

</$fill>
</$transclude>
